     :dp:`fls_z22std1crl49`
     A :t:`recursive type` is a :t:`type` whose contained :t:`[type]s` refer back to
     the containing :t:`type`, either directly or by referring to another :t:`type`
     which refers back to the original :t:`recursive type`.

