Details
- Added glossary-only `refutability` and migrated refutable pattern/constant/type in `src/patterns.rst`.
- Migrated referent, register/argument/class/name/expression/parameter terms in `src/ownership-and-deconstruction.rst` and `src/inline-assembly.rst`.
- Migrated remainder assignment/expression and repeat operand in `src/expressions.rst`.
- Added glossary-only `renaming` in `src/entities-and-resolution.rst`.
- Left `repetition operator` for the next batch (reverted its migration) in `src/macros.rst`.

